PRIVACY & DATA

Conversation data is transmitted to Anthropic's API under the user's own
API key and is subject to Anthropic's terms of service and privacy policy.
This tool does not independently store, log, or transmit conversation
content beyond the active browser session. API keys are session-only and
are never written to persistent storage.

